title: NFL Week 5 Preview
description:
Laura Rutledge and the NFL Live Crew discuss this weekend’s NFL slate, Russell Wilson’s rough start to the season, how the Rams will fare against the Cowboys’ defense and Field gives some fantasy football tips for this weekend.
